ncompatibility between the two hooks. LLM-DEP: No AI/ML. Rejection of System: if both hooks are importable Python modules, an in-process tmpdir roundtrip catches the format contract failure without spawning subprocesses. Rejection of Unit: the bug exists at the boundary between two distinct hook modules — a single module test cannot catch a write-format / read-format mismatch.","test_description":"Using a shared temporary directory: (1) invoke the PostToolUse hook's state-write path with a detected PR-create trigger to produce the gate state file; (2) invoke the pre-tool enforcement hook's read-and-enforce path pointing at the same directory; assert that the enforcement hook correctly identifies the gate as active and would block tool use, confirming the written format is parseable and actionable by the enforcer.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":null,"level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.04,"Integration":0.58,"System":0.32,"Agentic":0.04,"Workflow":0.02}}]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":9932,"cache_read_input_tokens":3199,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":9932},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"fc5a21d8-4f44-4d10-a94a-d88b87dcdd67","uuid":"de28f4a9-2a54-40fc-a21d-c65347891b4b"}
